songs.full_title: Big Spender by Theophilus London (Ft. A$AP Rocky)
songs.title: Big Spender

description.plain: After this video dropped of A$AP Rocky and Theophilus London kicking it and spitting over a nasty instrumental (which Theo had recycled from an older version of the song,) a major buzz circled the internet. During SXSW 2012, Theo and Pretty Flacko performed the song and it was a hit. The track samples Peggy Lee’s “Big Spender.”
